OL,3,C'Busiest year' on record for coastguard
OL,5,FA south Wales coastguard has said that
OL,6,Fthis year has officially been its
OL,7,Fbusiest on record.
OL,9,FPort Talbot Coastguard was called out
OL,10,Fon Friday (29 August) to reports of a
OL,11,Fpaddleboarder in difficulty off Newton
OL,12,FPoint near Porthcawl.
OL,14,FThe emergency service team said the
OL,15,Fincident marked a record-breaking
OL,16,Fnumber of attendance requests this
OL,17,Fyear.
OL,19,FThe paddleboarder had drifted
OL,20,Foffshore, and a nearby kayaker
OL,21,Fattempted to assist.
