OL,3,C'Busiest year' on record for coastguard
OL,5,FIn a social media post, Port Talbot
OL,6,FCoastguard said: "A member of the
OL,7,Fpublic acted appropriately by dialling
OL,8,F999 and requesting the Coastguard.
OL,9,FWhile en route, we received
OL,10,Fconfirmation that the paddleboarder
OL,11,Fhad safely made it back to shore
OL,12,Fwithout requiring any casualty care.
OL,14,F"This incident comes during what is
OL,15,Fnow officially our busiest year on
OL,16,Frecord for Port Talbot Coastguard."
OL,18,FIt comes after a "major incident" last
OL,19,Fweekend when six children were rescued
OL,20,Fby the team after they had got into
OL,21,F'serious difficulty' in the sea.
